# 詞: 睇怕

1. 個天烏沉沉咁，睇怕今晚會落大雨。 (The sky is dark and gloomy; it looks like it will rain heavily tonight.)
2. 佢成日唔見人影，睇怕係請假返鄉下探親。 (He hasn't been seen around for days; he's probably on leave to visit his family in the countryside.)
3. 呢間餐廳生意咁好，睇怕要排隊等好耐。 (This restaurant is so popular; it looks like we'll have to queue for a long time.)
4. 佢個樣睇落好攰，睇怕係昨晚通宵趕工。 (He looks very tired; it seems he stayed up all night working on a deadline.)
5. 呢部車舊舊哋，睇怕維修費用會好貴。 (This car is quite old; it looks like the repair costs will be very high.)
6. 佢對你咁客氣，睇怕係有求於你。 (He is being so polite to you; it looks like he wants something from you.)
7. 呢條路封咗，睇怕我哋要遲到。 (This road is closed; it looks like we're going to be late.)
8. 佢個個都唔理，睇怕係氣壞了。 (He's ignoring everyone; it looks like he's really angry.)
9. 呢件衫洗過之後縮咗水，睇怕唔合身。 (This shirt shrank after washing; it looks like it won't fit anymore.)
10. 佢成日發呆，睇怕係有心事。 (He's been spacing out all day; it looks like he has something on his mind.) [end of text]


